          "style": "First slide is one calm, authoritative 'stop before you sign' style hook. Body slides each expose one hidden cost or overlooked check with a concrete number and a clear next step. Myth-busting, protective, first-time-buyer friendly — readable and native to TikTok slideshow memes.",
          "narrative": "before you fall in love with the kitchen, check this number\nthe monthly payment is not the full cost of owning this home\nstop before you waive this as a first-time buyer\nyou got pre-approved — don't start shopping until you understand this\na low price can still be an expensive house\nthe biggest homebuying mistake is letting urgency replace the math",
